            "title": "【Hexo】使用Hexo搭建属于自己的博客",
            "date_published": "2023-07-05T03:23:20.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"hexo使用hexo搭建属于自己的博客\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#hexo使用hexo搭建属于自己的博客\">#</a> 【Hexo】使用 Hexo 搭建属于自己的博客</h1>\n<h1 id=\"\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#hexo%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2\">#</a> 【Hexo】使用 Hexo 搭建属于自己的博客</h1>\n<p><strong>目录</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t0\">一、查询当前博客发布地址</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t1\">二、域名注册</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t2\">1、这里博主以阿里云为例，首先进入阿里云官网，登录账号</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t3\">2、点击搜索按钮，搜索栏输入域名，点击搜索</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t4\">3、点击域名注册</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t5\">4、在搜索栏输入想要的域名，这里以 “wanwang” 举例，点击查询域名</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t6\">5、购买域名</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t7\">6、购买完成后，返回查询域名页面，点击管理我的域名</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t8\">7、找到刚刚购买的域名，点击解析</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t9\">8、点击添加记录</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t10\">9、添加记录</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t11\">10、设置成功后，等待状态变为正常即可</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t12\">11、设置自定义域名</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t13\">三、完成</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#t14\">1、访问刚才设置好的域名，“http:// 域名”，出现博客页面，表示成功。</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"-2\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-2\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#%E4%B8%80-%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80\">#</a> 一、查询当前博客发布地址</h1>\n<p>1、登录 GitHub，找到仓库（一般以 “.github.io” 结尾），点击进入</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/f16f4f455be5402f9b95487ac16f362c.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/f16f4f455be5402f9b95487ac16f362c.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/f16f4f455be5402f9b95487ac16f362c.png\">img</a></p>\n<p>2、右上方点击 “Settings”, 左下方找到 “Pages” 点击后，蓝色字体为博客发布的网址，点击查看，网址一般为 “<a href=\"https://xn--5mq40k5uk/%E2%80%9D\">https:// 仓库名 /”</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/e4b93952287a4830a07ef974e72890b3.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/e4b93952287a4830a07ef974e72890b3.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/e4b93952287a4830a07ef974e72890b3.png\">img</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"-3\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-3\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#%E4%BA%8C-%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C\">#</a> 二、域名注册</h1>\n<p>注：博主这里提供国内域名商的官网，仅供参考！</p>\n<p>阿里云网址</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.aliyun.com/\">阿里云 - 上云就上阿里云<img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/icon-default.png\" alt=\"img\">https://www.aliyun.com/</a></p>\n<p>华为云网址</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://activity.huaweicloud.com/\">最新优惠活动_云服务器特惠促销_打折云产品专场_特价低至 1 折 - 华为云<img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/icon-default.png\" alt=\"img\">https://activity.huaweicloud.com/</a></p>\n<p>腾讯云网址</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cloud.tencent.com/\">腾讯云 - 产业智变 云启未来<img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/icon-default.png\" alt=\"img\">https://cloud.tencent.com/</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-4\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-4\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#1-%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E5%8D%9A%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%A5%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E4%B8%BA%E4%BE%8B%E9%A6%96%E5%85%88%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E5%AE%98%E7%BD%91%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7\">#</a> 1、这里博主以阿里云为例，首先进入阿里云官网，登录账号</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/c294e851d3734e508c7aa093d656d2d1.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/c294e851d3734e508c7aa093d656d2d1.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/c294e851d3734e508c7aa093d656d2d1.png\">img</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-5\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-5\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#2-%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%8C%89%E9%92%AE%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%A0%8F%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2\">#</a> 2、点击搜索按钮，搜索栏输入域名，点击搜索</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/2e3c87e917e047b68e69a5ecc6809576.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/2e3c87e917e047b68e69a5ecc6809576.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/2e3c87e917e047b68e69a5ecc6809576.png\">img</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-6\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-6\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#3-%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C\">#</a> 3、点击域名注册</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/0176ff2c3e104636b5c938a075f94101.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/0176ff2c3e104636b5c938a075f94101.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/0176ff2c3e104636b5c938a075f94101.png\">img</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-7\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-7\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#\">#</a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"-8\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-8\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#4-%E5%9C%A8%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%A0%8F%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%83%B3%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E4%BB%A5wanwang%E4%B8%BE%E4%BE%8B%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D\">#</a> 4、在搜索栏输入想要的域名，这里以 “wanwang” 举例，点击查询域名</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/ad6c7f9be87d4d4f877d2ddc145be9e8.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/ad6c7f9be87d4d4f877d2ddc145be9e8.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/ad6c7f9be87d4d4f877d2ddc145be9e8.png\">img</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-9\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-9\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#5-%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D\">#</a> 5、购买域名</h2>\n<p>搜索结果，可能出现已注册情况，建议选择未注册的域名，点击购买，各位朋友请根据自己的需求和自身的经济实力购买，域名没有永久的都是有时效性的，具体可以询问客服</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/b761760294024ec5a015ba17b6e5256d.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/b761760294024ec5a015ba17b6e5256d.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/b761760294024ec5a015ba17b6e5256d.png\">img</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-10\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-10\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#6-%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E5%90%8E%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D\">#</a> 6、购买完成后，返回查询域名页面，点击管理我的域名</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/cfb0a55c15da4c99b4cf2054d01fe56c.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/cfb0a55c15da4c99b4cf2054d01fe56c.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/cfb0a55c15da4c99b4cf2054d01fe56c.png\">img</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-11\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-11\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#7-%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%88%9A%E5%88%9A%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90\">#</a> 7、找到刚刚购买的域名，点击解析</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/14a5a0a258914d078026d0e188c2d52b.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/14a5a0a258914d078026d0e188c2d52b.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/14a5a0a258914d078026d0e188c2d52b.png\">img</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-12\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-12\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#8-%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\">#</a> 8、点击添加记录</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/8ae1f0fd8ffa4c07a5a1c6c7ca0a52e4.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/8ae1f0fd8ffa4c07a5a1c6c7ca0a52e4.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/8ae1f0fd8ffa4c07a5a1c6c7ca0a52e4.png\">img</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-13\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-13\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#9-%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\">#</a> 9、添加记录</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/ddcaacbaca9f440e98bd8f690d667b2d.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/ddcaacbaca9f440e98bd8f690d667b2d.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/ddcaacbaca9f440e98bd8f690d667b2d.png\">img</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-14\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-14\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#10-%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E5%90%8E%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%BA%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF\">#</a> 10、设置成功后，等待状态变为正常即可</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/642fe813a4ab43339a94a23261f58d28.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/642fe813a4ab43339a94a23261f58d28.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/642fe813a4ab43339a94a23261f58d28.png\">img</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"-15\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-15\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#11-%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D\">#</a> 11、设置自定义域名</h2>\n<p>右上方点击 “Settings”，左下方找到 “Pages” 点击后，在 “Custom domain”（自定义域名）下方文本栏中填写域名，勾选 “Enforce HTTPS”（强制使用 https 协议），点击 “Save”（保存），蓝色字体为博客发布的网址，点击查看，网址一般为 “<a href=\"https://xn--eqrt2g/%E2%80%9D\">https:// 域名 /”</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/df5af9f92fc44565b3be43e426b50cee.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/df5af9f92fc44565b3be43e426b50cee.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/df5af9f92fc44565b3be43e426b50cee.png\">img</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"-16\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-16\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#%E4%B8%89-%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90\">#</a> 三、完成</h1>\n<h2 id=\"-17\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-17\">#</a> <a href=\"https://brath.top/2021/12/09/%E3%80%90HEXO%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/#1-%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E5%88%9A%E6%89%8D%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8Dhttp%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F\">#</a> 1、访问刚才设置好的域名，“<a href=\"http://xn--eqrt2g/\">http:// 域名</a>”，出现博客页面，表示成功。</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/30baf16189c9448da5e343f87759774a.png\"><img src=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/30baf16189c9448da5e343f87759774a.png\" alt=\"img\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brath4.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/picgo/30baf16189c9448da5e343f87759774a.png\">img</a></p>\n",
